<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Gapat Bot — Privacy Policy</title>
<link rel="icon" href="/img/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
<script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/alpinejs@3.x.x/dist/cdn.min.js"></script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
<style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');</style>
</head>
<body style="background:var(--bg-base);color:var(--text-primary)" x-data="{}" x-init="$store.user.init()">
 <script src="/js/app.js"></script>

 <%- include('partials/sidebar') %>

 <div class="main-content min-h-screen flex flex-col" :class="{ 'full': !$store.app.sidebarOpen }">
 <header class="sticky top-0 z-30 px-4 md:px-8 py-4 flex items-center gap-4" style="background:var(--header-bg);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-color);backdrop-filter:blur(12px)">
 <button @click="$store.app.toggleSidebar()" class="p-2 -ml-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-[var(--hover-bg)]">
 <i class="fas fa-bars text-xl"></i>
 </button>
 <h1 class="text-xl font-bold" style="color:var(--text-primary)">Privacy Policy</h1>
 </header>

 <!-- Content -->
 <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
 <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
 <p class="text-sm mb-10" style="color:var(--text-muted)">Last updated: July 2026</p>

 <div class="space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color:var(--text-secondary)">
 <section>
 <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color:var(--text-primary)">1. Data We Collect</h2>
 <p>Gapat Bot collects the following data to provide services:</p>
 <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1" style="color:var(--text-muted)">
 <li><strong style="color:var(--text-primary)">Discord User ID</strong> — to identify users</li>
 <li><strong style="color:var(--text-primary)">Server/Guild ID</strong> — to manage per-server configuration</li>
 <li><strong style="color:var(--text-primary)">Chat messages</strong> — processed to provide AI responses (not stored permanently)</li>
 <li><strong style="color:var(--text-primary)">Username & Avatar</strong> — for display on the dashboard</li>
 <li><strong style="color:var(--text-primary)">Usage data</strong> — message count, tokens, and active channels</li>
 </ul>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color:var(--text-primary)">2. How Data Is Used</h2>
 <p>The data collected is used to:</p>
 <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1" style="color:var(--text-muted)">
 <li>Run AI chatbot features on Discord servers</li>
 <li>Provide monitoring dashboard and analytics</li>
 <li>Manage server configuration and preferences</li>
 <li>Improve bot performance and security</li>
 <li>Prevent abuse and spam</li>
 </ul>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color:var(--text-primary)">3. Data Storage</h2>
 <p>Data is stored in a secure MongoDB database. We do not store chat message contents permanently — messages are only processed in real-time to generate AI responses. Server configuration data is stored as long as the bot is active on that server.</p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color:var(--text-primary)">4. Data Sharing</h2>
 <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third parties. Data is only used for the operation of the Gapat bot.</p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color:var(--text-primary)">5. Security</h2>
 <p>We implement standard security measures to protect data from unauthorized access, including connection encryption and secure token storage.</p>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color:var(--text-primary)">6. User Rights</h2>
 <p>You have the right to:</p>
 <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1" style="color:var(--text-muted)">
 <li>Request deletion of your account data</li>
 <li>Remove the bot from your server to stop data collection</li>
 <li>Contact us with questions regarding personal data</li>
 </ul>
 </section>

 <section>
 <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3" style="color:var(--text-primary)">7. Contact</h2>
 <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us through our Discord support server or the listed email.</p>
 </section>
 </div>
 </div>

 </div>
</body>
</html>
